  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To assess the effectiveness and security of a mobile App (beta version) for self-managing&#xD;
      emotional crisis in a pragmatic randomized controlled trial with 80 patients with borderline&#xD;
      personality disorder (40 patients with treatment as usual, TAU) versus 40 patients with TAU&#xD;
      plus the mobile App)&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
